general.desc: Wong Fong Industries Ltd is a provider of land transport engineering solutions and systems for the logistics, construction, waste management and defense industries. The group's operating segments are Engineering and Training. It generates revenue through the sale of cranes and other truck-mounted equipment including customization, engineering and installation of products and solutions for sale.
general.short_desc: Wong Fong Industries Ltd is a land transport engineering solutions and systems provider. It is engaged in the sale and installation of equipment; design, customization, engineering and integration of equipment; and repair services.
